Mr. Vincent J. Kaminski

Managing Director

Enron Capital & Trade Resources Corp.


Dear Mr. Kaminski:


Recently, there has been a lot of discussion and confusion on the

direction of the distributed energy (DE) industry. With the summer stock

price collapse and slow market development, many DE stakeholders are

re-thinking their strategies. Cambridge Energy Research Associates

(CERA) is as well.


In an effort to provide you with the most up-to-date, valued

information, CERA is asking each member of our Distributed Energy

Advisory Service to complete a brief survey so that we may better serve

you.  The survey can be found at the following link:

http://www.cera.com/survey/distributed


This survey is anonymous and all comments are welcome. We plan to

present and discuss the results at our Executive Retreat in Santa Fe,

New Mexico, December 5-7, 2001.


Thank you for your time and we appreciate your input.


Sincerely,


Steven Taub

Director, Distributed Energy


